sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (SUT)
    participant CS as Central System (Tool)

    Note over CP,CS: Memory State: RenewChargePointCertificate (CSMS-Section3, Table 120, p.107/176)
    Note over CP,CS: OCPP 1.6J (Security Extension)
    Note over CS: Config: CpoName is <Configured Vendor Name>

    CS->>CP: 1. ExtendedTriggerMessage.req
    Note left of CS: requestedMessage = SignChargePointCertificate<br/>connectorId = <Omitted>

    CP-->>CS: 2. ExtendedTriggerMessage.conf
    Note over CP: Validation: status should be Accepted

    Note over CP: Charge Point generates new<br/>public/private key pair and CSR

    CP->>CS: 3. SignCertificate.req
    Note right of CP: (doc does not list fields;<br/>expected: csr = <PEM-encoded CSR>)

    CS-->>CP: 4. SignCertificate.conf
    Note left of CS: status = Accepted

    Note over CS: Certificate Authority<br/>signs the certificate

    CS->>CP: 5. CertificateSigned.req
    Note left of CS: (doc does not list fields;<br/>expected: certificateChain = <PEM-encoded chain>)

    CP-->>CS: 6. CertificateSigned.conf
    Note over CP: Validation: status should be Accepted
    Note over CP: Charge Point verifies the validity<br/>of the signed certificate

    Note over CP,CS: State is RenewChargePointCertificate
